      casablanca_medina: "\"The old soul of the modern metropolis, where the stories of yesterday still breathe in the narrow streets.\"",
      chefchaouen_kasbah: "\"A crimson heart in a cerulean world, guarding the secrets of the Rif.\"",
      chefchaouen_spanish_mosque: "\"From this height, the blue city looks like a fallen piece of the sky.\"",
